{"word":"G4206 - πόῤῥω - pórrhō - por'-rho - Far","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πόῤῥω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pórrhō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">por'-rho</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Far</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தூரமாய், அப்புறம் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"far, at a distance, a great way off"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a>; <i>forwards</i>, that is, <i>at a distance</i>: - far, a great way off. See also <a href=\"#/G4207 - πόῤῥωθεν - pórrhōthen - por'-rho-then/4207\">G4207</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}